  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>To cast this jutsu the target must have at least 1 rank of Bleeding. You swing your blade into the opponent's bleeding wound, ripping it out and making it fester. Make a melee Taijutsu attack, on a hit you deal 7d6 slashing damage and the target suffers 1 rank of exhaustion for one minute. This Jutsu has a critical threat range of 19-20.</p><p>If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 2, increase the damage die by 1 step. If this jutsu is cast as a Chain 3 increase the damage die by +3</p><p>At Higher Ranks: For each rank you cast this jutsu above B-Rank, increase the cost of this jutsu by 3 and the damage by 1d6.</p>",
